{
  "stem": "20142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You had to-- if you hesitated, if you would ask, oh, is this [? at ?] [? so-- ?] that was not good.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would take the bottles away from you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to respond immediately without any hesitation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "15 bottles a day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was when I was very, very satisfied after being able to deliver for a number of days these bottles, until one day there was a raid and, accidentally, I got involved in it.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then got caught by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, for about four to six months, probably six months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was even--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "During the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even the ghetto was established, I had the possibility of getting with the work in columns from the ghetto, and disappear and do my work, come back with the working column back together.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were payoffs.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the foremen of such column knew who will join where and when.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Working column, return to the ghetto with the working column.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to be, be always ready to return to the ghetto at the proper time, otherwise I couldn't join in on the column.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was not a simple assignment, but it was very gratifying, very happy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can't imagine my mother's heart when I was returning home from-- from such mission.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, she did, and she approved of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we started to hear all the atrocities of Germans doing to the Jewish people, and then we decided that this is perhaps the one way of fighting back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it somehow worked out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, I also [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] joined the Hashomer Hatzair [INAUDIBLE] and this is the first time that I met [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anielewicz. ?] And--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1940.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
